data.description: ALL ELECTRIC RANCH STYLE HOME WITH FOUR BEDROOMS in Gainesville. This home has over an acre lot in a cul-de-sac.  Bedrooms are spacious. Vaulted Family Room with Fireplace. Kitchen has eat-in area, stained cabinets, pantry. Master Bedroom Suite has walk in closet. Master Bathroom has garden tub and separate shower.  Relax on the patio overlooking the private backyard. Two car garage. Why rent when you can own your own home. Call today!
